 7. SSO  (2 endpoints)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

sso-saml
  GET    → initiates SAML redirect                 Auth: none
  POST   → SAML assertion consumer (ACS)           Auth: none
  Env:   SSO_SAML_CERT, SSO_SAML_ENTRY_POINT
  → On success: issues JWT, redirects to IDE

sso-oidc
  GET    → initiates OIDC redirect                 Auth: none
  Callback handled in same function
  Env:   SSO_OIDC_CLIENT_ID, SSO_OIDC_CLIENT_SECRET, SSO_OIDC_ISSUER
  → On success: issues JWT, redirects to IDE


