 AI GATEWAY
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

 Gateway: XnthGateway (kAIxuGateway13) at https://skyesol.netlify.app
 Auth:    Authorization: Bearer $KAIXU_VIRTUAL_KEY

 CORS rule: skyesol.netlify.app does NOT return CORS headers on OPTIONS.
            Browser apps must NEVER call it directly.
            All AI calls go through same-origin Netlify proxy functions:

   Browser/IDE  →  /.netlify/functions/gateway-chat    → skyesol gateway-chat
   Browser/IDE  →  /.netlify/functions/gateway-stream  → skyesol gateway-stream
   Browser/IDE  →  /.netlify/functions/gateway-embed   → skyesol gateway-embed

 Local dev: /api/* redirect in netlify.toml proxies to skyesol.netlify.app

 Chat request shape (to gateway-chat / gateway-stream):
   { provider: "openai"|"anthropic"|"gemini",
     model: "string",
     messages: [{role:"system"|"user"|"assistant", content:"text"}],
     max_tokens: 8192,
     temperature: 0 }

 Chat response (non-streaming):
   { output_text, provider, model, usage:{input_tokens,output_tokens,cost_cents},
     month:{month,cap_cents,spent_cents} }

 Streaming SSE events:
   meta:  { provider, model, month:{month,cap_cents,spent_cents} }
   delta: { text }
   done:  { usage:{...}, month:{...} }
   error: { error }

 Embed request shape (to gateway-embed):
   { provider: "gemini", model: "gemini-embedding-001",
     input: "text"|["text1","text2"],
     taskType: "RETRIEVAL_QUERY"|"RETRIEVAL_DOCUMENT",
     outputDimensionality: 1536 }

 Embed response:
   { embeddings: [[float,...]], dimensions: 1536, usage, month }

 IDE branded model names → XnthGateway mapping:
   kAIxU-flash  → provider: gemini,    model: gemini-2.5-flash            (Free/Pro)
   kAIxU-pro    → provider: anthropic, model: claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022  (Team/Enterprise)
   (override via env: KAIXU_FLASH_PROVIDER/MODEL, KAIXU_PRO_PROVIDER/MODEL)

 Error codes surfaced to user:
   402 → "Monthly cap reached" — block calls until upgrade/top-up
   429 → rate limit — retry guidance
   401 → invalid/revoked virtual key


